<br>
The classic method of reaching POM without a raid is to get non-KOS to COV, then use various divine aura items or spells to blitz up to POM -- hopefully before dying.  Note that on FV, no one can bind in POM. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fahrner>fahrner</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/17/03 2:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=665.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Slight misconception there</span><hr size=1>  Hehe, my corpse now sits at the PoM zone pyramid. i died right before clicking on it <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=enheduannalia>EnheduannaLia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/17/03 8:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=665.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Slight misconception there</span><hr size=1> What gives +GOV faction? I was going to guess Vulak, but that doesn't really make sense. I suppose it could be Yelinak, because I always /quit before he died so I don't know what faction adjustments he has. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=manouk>Manouk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/17/03 6:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboar